<h3><a id="concepts" name="concepts"></a>1.
Concepts</h3>
<blockquote>
  <p>This project is designed to
get you started querying MySQL databases with PHP. You will learn these
concepts:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Connect to the MySQL
server from a PHP script<br>
    </li>
    <li>Select a MySQL database to
query<br>
    </li>
    <li>Query a table from the
database using SQL<br>
    </li>
    <li>Fetch the query result set
row by row using a loop<br>
    </li>
    <li>Process the column values
of each row<br>
    </li>
    <li>Format the data&nbsp;
using HTML tags to output to a web
page<br>
    </li>
  </ul>
</blockquote>
